a) recognition of the aircraft identification in a SSR and/or MLAT label;

b) recognition of an assigned discrete code, the setting of which has been

verified, in a SSR and/or MLAT label;

c) direct recognition of the aircraft identification of a Mode S-equipped aircraft
in a SSR and/or MLAT label;

d) _ by transfer of identification;
e) observation of compliance with an instruction to set a specific code;
